x_n=\left(1-\frac{1}{3}\right)^2\cdot\left(1-\frac{1}{6}\right)^2\cdot\left(1-\frac{1}{10}\right)^2\cdot\left(1-\frac{1}{15}\right)^2\cdots\left(1-\frac{1}{\frac{n(n+1)}{2}}\right)^2  \quad    ,n\geq2                   
\lim_ {n\to\infty} x_n
\ln x_n\to 0
\sum_{n=1}^\infty  \frac{2}{n(n+1)} = 2\not\to +\infty,
\left(1-\frac{1}{\frac{n(n+1)}{2}}\right)^2=(1-\frac{2}{n+1}+\frac{2}{n})^2=(1-\frac{2}{n+1}+\frac{2}{n})(1+\frac{2}{n+1}-\frac{2}{n})
(1-\frac{1}{\frac{n(n+1)}{2}})^2 =\frac{(n-1)(n+2)}{n(n+1)}
